Executable binary rsa_genkey and rsa_sign both are built from polarssl-1.3.4-gpl.tgz.

You can apply below patches to get those tools,
    patches/001-program-rsa-sign-use-sha256-instead-of-sha1.patch
    patches/002-program-rsa-genkey-key-length-2048-instead-of-1024.patch
    patches/003-program-rsa-sign-specify-priv-key.patch
    patches/004-program-rsa-genkey-c-type.patch

